title: on_idle()
brief: Called when the client is idle.
seealso: on_exit, on_key, on_read_message
----

<p>If you define the function <span class="tt">on_idle</span> it will be regularly called when the client is idle, currently this is approximately once a second.</p>
<p>For example:</p>
<pre>
function on_idle()
   <a href="msg.html">msg</a>( "The client is idle " .. os.date() );
end
</pre>